   <db:para>The Universal Style is based on the Microsoft Universal Design Guidelines. <db:link xlink:href="qtquickcontrols2-universal.html#detailed-desc-universal" xrefstyle="page" annotations="detailed-desc-universal">More...</db:link>
   </db:para>
